Holes or tears amended on fols. 3, 14, 22, 23, 28, 61.&#xD;
Small holes are visible on the spine fold of the quires and on the front and back board; the boards have been attached to the Ms. upside down; the boards have either been reattached in the wrong way after restoration or originate from another Ms.</condition>
